<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<%- include('partials/head', { title: 'Announcements - the grid' }) %>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/sidebar', { currentPath: '/dashboard/announcements' }) %>

    <div class="main-wrapper">
        <div class="top-bar">
            <h1 class="page-title">Announcements System</h1>
        </div>

        <main class="main-content">
            <p style="color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 32px;">Verwalte die Twitch-Streamer und YouTube-Kanäle, die automatisch in Kanal <code style="color: var(--accent-color);">1294799305357660214</code> angekündigt werden sollen.</p>

            <% if (typeof errorMsg !== 'undefined' && errorMsg) { %>
                <div class="alert alert-error"><i class="fa-solid fa-triangle-exclamation"></i> <%= errorMsg %></div>
            <% } %>

            <div class="stats-grid">
                <!-- TWITCH -->
                <div class="panel" style="margin-bottom: 0;">
                    <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 24px; padding-bottom: 16px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--glass-border);">
                        <i class="fa-brands fa-twitch" style="font-size: 24px; color: #9146FF;"></i>
                        <h2 style="margin: 0;">Twitch Livestreams</h2>
                    </div>

                    <div style="margin-bottom: 24px;">
                        <% if (config.twitch.length === 0) { %>
                            <div style="color: var(--text-muted); font-style: italic; font-size: 14px;">Keine Twitch-Streamer eingetragen.</div>
                        <% } else { %>
                            <% config.twitch.forEach(function(username) { %>
                                <div style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border: 1px solid var(--glass-border); border-radius: 8px; padding: 12px 16px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 8px;">
                                    <span style="font-weight: 500;"><%= username %></span>
                                    <form action="/dashboard/announcements/remove" method="POST" style="margin:0;">
                                        <input type="hidden" name="type" value="twitch">
                                        <input type="hidden" name="id" value="<%= username %>">
                                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-outline" style="padding: 4px 10px; font-size: 12px; color: var(--danger); border-color: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.3);"><i class="fa-solid fa-trash"></i></button>
                                    </form>
                                </div>
                            <% }); %>
                        <% } %>
                    </div>

                    <form action="/dashboard/announcements/add" method="POST" style="display: flex; gap: 8px;">
                        <input type="hidden" name="type" value="twitch">
                        <input type="text" name="id" class="form-control" style="flex: 1;" placeholder="Benutzername (z.B. montanablack)" required>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary"><i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i></button>
                    </form>
                </div>

                <!-- YOUTUBE -->
                <div class="panel" style="margin-bottom: 0;">
                    <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 24px; padding-bottom: 16px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--glass-border);">
                        <i class="fa-brands fa-youtube" style="font-size: 24px; color: #FF0000;"></i>
                        <h2 style="margin: 0;">YouTube Videos</h2>
                    </div>

                    <div style="margin-bottom: 24px;">
                        <% if (config.youtube.length === 0) { %>
                            <div style="color: var(--text-muted); font-style: italic; font-size: 14px;">Keine YouTube-Kanäle eingetragen.</div>
                        <% } else { %>
                            <% config.youtube.forEach(function(channelId) { %>
                                <div style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border: 1px solid var(--glass-border); border-radius: 8px; padding: 12px 16px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 8px;">
                                    <span style="font-family: monospace; font-size: 12px; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3); padding: 4px; border-radius: 4px;"><%= channelId %></span>
                                    <form action="/dashboard/announcements/remove" method="POST" style="margin:0;">
                                        <input type="hidden" name="type" value="youtube">
                                        <input type="hidden" name="id" value="<%= channelId %>">
                                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-outline" style="padding: 4px 10px; font-size: 12px; color: var(--danger); border-color: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.3);"><i class="fa-solid fa-trash"></i></button>
                                    </form>
                                </div>
                            <% }); %>
                        <% } %>
                    </div>

                    <form action="/dashboard/announcements/add" method="POST" style="display: flex; gap: 8px;">
                        <input type="hidden" name="type" value="youtube">
                        <input type="text" name="id" class="form-control" style="flex: 1;" placeholder="@Name oder ID (z.B. @MontanaBlack)" required>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary"><i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i></button>
                    </form>
                    <p style="font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 12px;"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info"></i> Tipp: Du kannst einfach den <b>@Benutzernamen</b> eintragen. Das System wandelt ihn automatisch in die richtige ID um!</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </main>
        <%- include('partials/footer') %>
    </div>
</body>
</html>